    <title>Qt属性动画笔记</title>
    <url>/2022/02/11/Qt%E5%B1%9E%E6%80%A7%E5%8A%A8%E7%94%BB%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">set_animation</span>(<span class="params">self</span>):</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># logo动画</span></span><br><span class="line">    animation = QPropertyAnimation(self)</span><br><span class="line">    animation.setTargetObject(self)</span><br><span class="line">    animation.setPropertyName(<span class="string">b&quot;windowOpacity&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    animation.setStartValue(<span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    animation.setEndValue(<span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 动画时长</span></span><br><span class="line">    animation.setDuration(<span class="number">3000</span>)  <span class="comment"># 3s</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 设置动画曲线</span></span><br><span class="line">    animation.setEasingCurve(QEasingCurve.InQuart)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 开启动画</span></span><br><span class="line">    animation.start()</span><br><span class="line">    animation.finished.connect(<span class="keyword">lambda</span>: self.close())</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<ul>
<li><p>这里提供Qt官方的动画曲线预设</p>
<blockquote>
<p><a href="https://doc.qt.io/qtforpython-5/PySide2/QtCore/QEasingCurve.html?highlight=qeasingcurve">Qt动画曲线预设</a></p>
</blockquote>
</li>
</ul>
]]></content>
